imdb.plot outline: You Cancervive is dedicated to empowering young adult cancer fighters and survivors and will be raising awareness for young adults with cancer."You Cancervive", is the hour long t.v. series, hosted by young adult cancer survivor and YouTube sensation Racheli Alkobey, AKA "Radiant Racheli".
